{"tid":163204,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"換氣過度症候群","createTime":"2017-03-19T18:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T18:03:17.000Z","uid":34529,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0bbd36e841deb161bb2aaf24523536c076d02b","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"情緒性呼吸困難<br />\n如因頭痛，換氣過度症候群，或者是歇斯底里症所造成大腦下視丘過度刺激下的呼吸困難。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲已經唔可以自己呼吸<br />\n我呢幾年都係咁 成日好緊張 好似唔夠氣<br />\n我啲手動呼吸聲比人話係羅網（唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個日成日形住有人死有人有危險 返工比人鬧<br />\n有無人可以救我 我控制唔到我思想 同想自然呼吸<br />\n我好辛苦啊"},{"pid":"14ca38cdbeae834064d807074c54fcb6663d2cbd","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T18:50:35.000Z","msg":"以前睇過急症 但查唔出 <br />\n幾年後先自己搵到類似病症"},{"pid":"550e82e0ec2257445178c037005587d80e0f168f","tid":163204,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T18:54:48.000Z","msg":"會唔會可能你有驚恐症？<br />\n因為某啲驚恐症都會有你呢啲症狀<br />\n建議你搵個專科醫生睇睇"},{"pid":"70abd7139f76e1cd2a5e078f495839342478387f","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會可能你有驚恐症？<br />\n因為某啲驚恐症都會有你呢啲症狀<br />\n建議你搵個專科醫生睇睇</blockquote><br />\n有無好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1eb9c0994655aacbcd68a6f1b48671bb264ad1","tid":163204,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T20:21:52.000Z","msg":"試下yoga"},{"pid":"89328f8ce5d5b1b9748c04638c10c4bdcd0aab91","tid":163204,"uid":81220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T21:31:32.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係臨訓個陣<br />\n手動呼吸之餘仲要覺得唔夠氧氣<br />\n瘋狂深呼吸搞到過度換氣 仲手腳麻痺晒<br />\n入過一次急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫生話係心理問題<br />\n我就好啲 日頭通常無事 可以自動呼吸<br />\n多數臨訓 係戲院 個啲就會咁<br />\n依加都係因為咁所以仲未訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我會玩下電話分散注意力咁 但唔係次次得 搞到成日好夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87007d13f0f68f5dd2eb7c1c8e6f3cee251b346","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65cee6284de025fc4f3755c7d853fafc77b40600","tid":163204,"uid":55573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:23:17.000Z","msg":"我有時都有抖唔到氣既問題..<br />\n之後就急速抖氣 但就開始想暈想暈咁....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋講野唔可以太大聲 會唔夠氣咁"},{"pid":"a41877fe8fbea0afe6301bbb8ab03be45c0a6f6c","tid":163204,"uid":64553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"留名 以前有 宜家好番好多"},{"pid":"66c1e3e4b5c057ea548f98cea36af154703120fb","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 以前有 宜家好番好多</blockquote><br />\n點樣解決"},{"pid":"96cf4bd3eccbe0a54ec961449b00c812d19ef51f","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有時都有抖唔到氣既問題..<br />\n之後就急速抖氣 但就開始想暈想暈咁....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋講野唔可以太大聲 會唔夠氣咁</blockquote><br />\n我都係啊屌"},{"pid":"6422e4a17147e3b8a370e633a72fb8ce11e24a48","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下yoga</blockquote><br />\n一日一杯？有咩功效"},{"pid":"54502a3dc9ba213a1aff8a2a5087bf1b243d9583","tid":163204,"uid":64553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名 以前有 宜家好番好多</blockquote><br />\n點樣解決</blockquote><br />\n我諗係心態同環境問題<br />\n宜家好多野都順其自然"},{"pid":"53a6f496203e74615190f9d4af6172c8b7cfa2fa","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>