 />\n試下食綜合維他命 鈣片等等</blockquote><br />\n我有睇過一次精神科 不過怕比人捉入去<br />\n無再去睇"},{"pid":"a707d16e5fd4dd8bbdd805687ab27c231bae004f","tid":163204,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T17:23:11.000Z","msg":"有時 anxious 果陣 會咁<br />\n長期 咁 會respiratory  alkalosis"},{"pid":"b076b7a14b2f2e5f03a8b9d868c2774c711826c7","tid":163204,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"睇到呢個仆街post 就開始手動呼吸"},{"pid":"26144997d4edba298d46aed891905cbb9a0097d6","tid":163204,"uid":34529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T18:03:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到呢個仆街post 就開始手動呼吸</blockquote><br />\n都唔係我想嘅"}]}